quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Manjalo ngifunga ngokubekwa kwezinkanyezi
  56,76,Futhi ngempela yisifungo esikhulu ukube benazi
  56,77,Ngempela yona iyiQur’an ehloniphekile
  56,78,Encwadini elondolozekile
  56,79,Ayithintwa ngaphandle kwabamsulwa
  56,80,Isambulo esivela eNkosini yemihlaba
  56,81,Ngakube yileNkulumo yini nina eningakholelwa kuyona
  56,82,Futhi nenza isabelo senu ukuthi kube ukwenqaba kwenu
  56,83,Manjalo kungani uma (umphefumulo uphuma) ufinyelela emninzweni
  56,84,Futhi nina ngalesosikhathi nibhekile
  56,85,Futhi thina siseduzane kakhulu kuyena kunani kepha aniboni
  56,86,Manjalo kungani ningenzi – uma kungukuthi nina angeke nehlulelwe
  56,87,Wubuyiseleni emumvaumakungukuthininaningabaneqiniso
  56,88,Manjalo uma wayengomunye wabasondezwe eduzane
  56,89,Manjalo ukuphumula nezabelo kanye nesivande senjabulo
  56,90,Futhi uma engomunye wabangane bangakwesokunene
  56,91,"Ngakho-ke\tukuthula\tkungokwakho\tongowabangane bangakwesokunene"
  56,92,Futhi uma wayengomunye wabaphikayo abaphambukayo (eqinisweni)
  56,93,Manjalo ukujatshuliswa (kwakhe) amanzi abilayo
  56,94,Nokusha emlilweni wesihogo
  56,95,Ngempela lokhu yiqiniso langempela
  56,96,"Ngakho-ke dumisa igama leNkosi yakho, enkulu"
  57,1,KudumisauMvelinqangikonkeokusemazulwininasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  57,2,Ungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba uyaphilisa futhi uyabulala futhi yena wenza zonke izinto
  57,3,Yena ungowokuqala nowokugcina nosobala nosithele futhi yena uyisazi sazozonke izinto
  57,4,"Nguyena owadala amazulu nomhlaba ezinsukwini eziyisithupha wayesezibeka esihlalweni sobukhosi, wazi konke okungena emhlabeni nakho konke okuphuma kuwona kanye nakho konke okwehlela phansi okuphuma ezulwini nakho konke okunyukela khona futhi yena ukanye nani noma ngabe yikuphi lapho nikhona futhi uMvelinqangi uyakubona lokho enikwenzayo"
  57,5,Ungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi ikuMvelinqangi lapho zibuyiselwa khona izindaba
  57,6,Wenza ukuthi ubusuku bungenele emini futhi wenza ukuthi imini ingenele ebusuku futhi yena uyakwazi lokho okusezifubeni
  57,7,"Kholwani kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi nisebenzise kulokho anenza naba abalandelayo kukona, kepha labo abakholwayo phakathi kwenu futhi abasebenzisayo (abanikelayo) okwabo ngumvuzo omkhulu"
  57,8,Futhi kungani ningakholelwa kuMvelinqangi kanti isithunywa sinimemela ekukholelweni eNkosini yenu futhi yasithatha isivumelwano senu uma kungukuthi nina ningamakholwa
  57,9,Yena uyilowo owehlisela phezulu kwenceku yakhe amavesi acacile ukuze anikhiphe ebumnyameni aniyise ekukhanyeni futhi ngempela uMvelinqangi ngani umnene unesihawu
  57,10,"Futhi kungani ningasebenzisi endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi ngelikaMvelinqangi ifa lamazulu nomhlaba abalingani phakathi kwenu laba abasebenzisa ngaphambili kokunqoba futhi balwa, labo bakhulu kakhulu ngezinga kunalabo abasebenzisa ngamumva futhi balwa, futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo"
  57,11,Ngubani lowo ongaboleka uMvelinqangi ukuboleka okuhle ukuzeamphindelekonakabilibeseebanomvuzoohloniphekile
  57,12,Khumbula ngosuku uyobona abesilisa abakholwayo nabesifazane abakholwayo ukukhanya kwabo kuhamba ngaphambili kwabo futhi ngakwezokunene zabo izindaba zenu ezinhle namhlanje yizivande okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula bayohlala khona ingunaphakade lokho ukuphumelela okukhulu
  57,13,"Ngosuku lapho abazenzisi besilisa nabazenzisi besifazane beyothi kulabo abakholwayo “silindeni ukuze sithole okokukhanya kwenu” kuyothiwa “phindelani emumva ngemumva kwenu bese nifuna ukukhanya” manjalo kuyobekwa udonga phakathi kwabo olunesango ngaphakathi, ngaphakathi kunomusa kepha ngaphandle kwalo kunesijeziso"
  57,14,"Bayobamemeza (abangakholwanga bathi), “sasingeve yini sikanye nani?” bayothi, “yebo kepha nina naniyilinga imiphefumulo yenu futhi nalinda nangabaza kanye nemicabango eyanikhohlisa kwaze kwafika impoqo kaMvelinqangi futhi wanikhohlisa ngoMvelinqangi umkhohlisi (ongusathane)”"
  57,15,"Manjalo kulolusuku angeke yamukelwe kunina inhlengo futhi angeke (yamukelwe) kulabo abangakholwanga, indawo yenu yokuhlala umlilo wona ungumngane wenu futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona"